  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969860/extras/47fbf22e1b5454d2ed828006f13f7998.avif?t=1752570990\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>🎲A colorful cast of characters are waiting for you in MACHI KORO With Everyone!  </strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>With Remote Play Together support, players who own a copy can invite up to THREE friends to join in on all the fun! Roll the dice, get money, buy buildings and win!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>🎲What exactly is MACHI KORO With Everyone? </strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's the video game bundle that combines the classic board game Machi Koro, which has sold over a million copies worldwide, along with its sister game Machi Koro 2. Play offline, online with up to 4 players total. Family, friends and players around the world...everyone can join your game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>* \"Harbor\" and \"Millionaire's Row\" are not included</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>🎲Introduction to the Simple Rules of Machi Koro</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969860/extras/24438950cc51e74779fdf98c91849a1c.avif?t=1752570990\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969860/extras_big/24438950cc51e74779fdf98c91849a1c.avif?t=1752570990 width=800 height=283 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969860/extras/2249293ff4c3e72e9edcac643ee15671.avif?t=1752570990\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969860/extras_big/2249293ff4c3e72e9edcac643ee15671.avif?t=1752570990 width=800 height=665 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969860/extras/06a2894c0a683f12b6178908ffdaf279.avif?t=1752570990\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969860/extras_big/06a2894c0a683f12b6178908ffdaf279.avif?t=1752570990 width=800 height=382 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>🎲Various Ways to Play! Single & Multiplayer</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play with up to 4 people, both online and offline.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969860/extras/6a8d942b19263f3e9fbd4fbb5f258db3.avif?t=1752570990\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find Friends -You can invite friends from Steam to play. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find Guests - You can play exclusively with people who know the password you share via social media or other means. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random Match - You can play with players from around the world matched randomly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>* Each player needs their own hardware and software, unless the host invites a guest using Remote Play Together.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>* Cross-platform play is not supported.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Offline</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play against the CPU by yourself.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 to 4 players can play in local multiplayer.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*　Play while taking turns with multiple other players.</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969860/extras/47fbf22e1b5454d2ed828006f13f7998.avif?t=1752570990\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>🎲A colorful cast of characters are waiting for you in MACHI KORO With Everyone!  </strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>With Remote Play Together support, players who own a copy can invite up to THREE friends to join in on all the fun! Roll the dice, get money, buy buildings and win!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>🎲What exactly is MACHI KORO With Everyone? </strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's the video game bundle that combines the classic board game Machi Koro, which has sold over a million copies worldwide, along with its sister game Machi Koro 2. Play offline, online with up to 4 players total. Family, friends and players around the world...everyone can join your game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>* \"Harbor\" and \"Millionaire's Row\" are not included</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>🎲Introduction to the Simple Rules of Machi Koro</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969860/extras/24438950cc51e74779fdf98c91849a1c.avif?t=1752570990\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969860/extras_big/24438950cc51e74779fdf98c91849a1c.avif?t=1752570990 width=800 height=283 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969860/extras/2249293ff4c3e72e9edcac643ee15671.avif?t=1752570990\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969860/extras_big/2249293ff4c3e72e9edcac643ee15671.avif?t=1752570990 width=800 height=665 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969860/extras/06a2894c0a683f12b6178908ffdaf279.avif?t=1752570990\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969860/extras_big/06a2894c0a683f12b6178908ffdaf279.avif?t=1752570990 width=800 height=382 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>🎲Various Ways to Play! Single & Multiplayer</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play with up to 4 people, both online and offline.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1969860/extras/6a8d942b19263f3e9fbd4fbb5f258db3.avif?t=1752570990\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find Friends -You can invite friends from Steam to play. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find Guests - You can play exclusively with people who know the password you share via social media or other means. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random Match - You can play with players from around the world matched randomly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>* Each player needs their own hardware and software, unless the host invites a guest using Remote Play Together.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>* Cross-platform play is not supported.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Offline</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play against the CPU by yourself.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 to 4 players can play in local multiplayer.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*　Play while taking turns with multiple other players.</i></p>",
